summary: Qualified Primary School Teacher with a eleven-year long experience of working with children between the ages of 2 and 15 years old. I currently work as a Cover Teacher at the Amsterdam International Community School (AICS) in Amsterdam and during 2018 I worked as a Teacher at the Internationella Engelska Skolan (IES) in Stockholm. I graduated from the University of Crete in 2009 and obtained a Masters from the University of Cyprus in 2011. Since then I have worked in administrative, teaching and managerial positions at both Greek and English speaking schools in Cyprus, Greece, Sweden and the Netherlands. I am particularly interested in learning and gaining experience in diverse educational environments, systems and teaching approaches.
